{"id": "lrr1665702733764", "title": "PGS Connector Options", "breadcrumbs": ["DBMS Support", "Database Connectors", "PostgreSQL", "PGS Connector Options"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrr1665702733764.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">PGS Connector Options</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:  Load Definitions for PostgreSQL  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:  Load Definitions for PostgreSQL  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xeu1665702623836.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   map fixed length to variable \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   map fixed length to variable \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdg1665702961567.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrr1665702733764.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrr1665702733764.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrr1665702733764.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lrr1665702733764.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrr1665702733764.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrr1665702733764.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lrr1665702733764\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      PGS Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__pgs_connector_options_168586\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__topic_d57347e1_d57348e1_d57349e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__p_d57350e1_d57351e1_d57352e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            1}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__topic_d37817e1_d37818e1_d37819e1_d37820e1_d37821e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722052e74\">\n                       \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26132e1_d26133e1_d26134e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lca1665702725226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lca1665702725226.html\" title=\"Enable or disable testing for the existence of tables and stored procedures.\">checks</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26135e1_d26136e1_d26137e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rov1665702729225.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rov1665702729225.html\" title=\"Determines whether connection pooling is enabled.\">connection pooling</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26138e1_d26139e1_d26140e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twv1665702729296.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twv1665702729296.html\" title=\"Set the number of concurrent connections the connector is allowed to maintain.\">connections</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26141e1_d26142e1_d26143e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xcw1665702729440.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xcw1665702729440.html\" title=\"Specifies the case for table names.\">entity names</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26144e1_d26145e1_d26146e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xti1665702725693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xti1665702725693.html\" title=\"Specify whether statements remain open after a commit.\">hold statements</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26147e1_d26148e1_d26149e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vip1665702725886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vip1665702725886.html\" title=\"Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.\">identifiers</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26150e1_d26151e1_d26152e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fje1665702706365.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fje1665702706365.html\" title=\"Set a time-out period for all transaction and query requests.\">lock timeout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26153e1_d26154e1_d26155e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lge1665702664169.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lge1665702664169.html\" title=\"Set the cursor type to SQL_CURSOR_KEYSET_DRIVEN to improve performance when using the order by clause on large tables.\">keysetcursor</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26156e1_d26157e1_d26158e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zmh1665702705308.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zmh1665702705308.html\" title=\"Set the isolation level for the database transactions of the connector.\">lock isolation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26159e1_d26160e1_d26161e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mft1665702729839.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mft1665702729839.html\" title=\"Set the number of seconds to wait for a successful logon before yielding.\">logon timeout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26162e1_d26163e1_d26164e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdg1665702961567.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdg1665702961567.html\" title=\"Map fields with a fixed length storage format (CHAR) to a variable length storage format.\">map fixed length to variable</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26165e1_d26166e1_d26167e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xie1665702706126.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xie1665702706126.html\" title=\"Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\">maxlockwait</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26171e1_d26172e1_d26173e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jbg1665702730049.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbg1665702730049.html\" title=\"Specify whether the connector will use stored procedures to update, insert, delete, and fetch data, or use SQL instead.\">procedures</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26174e1_d26175e1_d26176e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnt1665702726651.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnt1665702726651.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface or the DBMS is responsible for maintaining referential integrity.\">ri</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26177e1_d26178e1_d26179e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pam1665702726925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pam1665702726925.html\" title=\"Specify whether segmented fields will be stored to large object data types.\">segmented fields</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26180e1_d26181e1_d26182e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"msy1665702733836.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msy1665702733836.html\" title=\"Include the entire Unicode range (SMP)\">smp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26183e1_d26184e1_d26185e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exm1665702661663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exm1665702661663.html\" title=\"Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26186e1_d26187e1_d26188e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aht1719471196112.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aht1719471196112.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface should enable or disable the Uniface cache mechanism for statements.\">stmtcache</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__topic_d37822e1_d37823e1_d37824e1_d37825e1_d37826e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722052e272\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__d6884e20\">Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__topic_d37827e1_d37828e1_d37829e1_d37830e1_d37831e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722052e281\">\n                       Syntax Rules</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__p_d57365e1_d57366e1_d57367e1\">The syntax rules for setting connector options\n\t\tare:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26189e1_d26190e1_d26191e1\">Options can be set using either a colon (<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>) or an equals sign (<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>). Thus\n\t\t\t <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> is the same as\n\t\t\t <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__p_d57368e1_d57369e1_d57370e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">ri:on</code> and\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">ri=on</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26192e1_d26193e1_d26194e1\">The total length of the assignment should not\n\t\t\t exceed 80 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26195e1_d26196e1_d26197e1\">Each option must be specified only once </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26198e1_d26199e1_d26200e1\">Multiple options must be separated by commas\n\t\t\t (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26201e1_d26202e1_d26203e1\">Words and numbers within each option are\n\t\t\t separated by one or more spaces or tabs </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrr1665702733764__li_d26204e1_d26205e1_d26206e1\">Options are not case-dependent </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Long format</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS = isolation=read uncommitted, entity names=upper</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Short format</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$PGS_PARAMS = iso:ru, ents:upper </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PGS Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 PGS Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$PGS_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$PGS_PARAMS Option { , Option 1} Options checks connection pooling connections entity names hold statements identifiers lock timeout keysetcursor lock isolation logon timeout map fixed length to variable maxlockwait procedures ri segmented fields smp step size stmtcache Description Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific. Syntax Rules The syntax rules for setting connector options are: Options can be set using either a colon ( : ) or an equals sign ( = ). Thus Option : Value is the same as Option = Value . For example: ri:on and ri=on . The total length of the assignment should not exceed 80 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options. Each option must be specified only once Multiple options must be separated by commas ( , ) Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs Options are not case-dependent Long format USYS$PGS_PARAMS = isolation=read uncommitted, entity names=upper Copy Short format USYS$PGS_PARAMS = iso:ru, ents:upper Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}